snippet.title: Interference: Dead Air | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
It's time to interfere! Interference: Dead Air is available now on Steam: http://bit.ly/InterferenceGame

Interference: Dead Air is a narrative–driven sci-fi thriller by developer Fear of Corn. All hell's breaking loose in a mysterious research facility and the only person who can save the day is the night shift security guard in the booth outside. Remotely control systems, guide scientists to safety or just… goof off? You’re not in danger. Yet.

Learn more at http://fearofcorn.com and http://publishvicarious.com

Copyright © 2023
